videos.description: Idaho's Mason Petrino's pass is deflected in the air and Leon McQuaker swoops in and completes the tip-drill interception.
videos.headline: McQuaker shakes the stadium with tip-drill pick

videos.description: New Mexico State turns a turnover into a quick 7 points as Larry Rose III takes the carry and bends it back up the middle 25 yards for the score.
videos.headline: Rose rips opening-drive TD run

videos.description: Colton Richardson connects with David Ungerer on a 25-yard dart to cut the deficit to 14-7.
videos.headline: Richardson's TD pass puts Vandals on board

videos.description: The Vandals break through the line to block the field  goal attempt to keep the game at 14-7.
videos.headline: Idaho storms the middle to block FG

videos.description: Idaho's Armond Hawkins comes down with the jump-ball in the end zone to give the Vandals the ball back trailing seven.
videos.headline: Red zone INT keeps Vandals in the game
